  "title": "Savory Oozy Greek Buckwheat Oven-Roasted Galaktoboureko",
  "description": "A savory and crispy greek dish featuring buckwheat flour with a touch of sweetness from honey. Perfect for brunch or as a snack, this dessert-like treat is both jain-friendly and smoke-hot.",
