  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 200°C.",
    "Mix flour, sugar, and salt in a large bowl.",
    "Gradually add beaten eggs while mixing until smooth dough forms.",
    "Fold in grated lemon zest and chopped parsley.",
    "Drop spoonfuls of batter onto a baking sheet lined with parchment paper.",
    "Bake for 20 minutes or until golden brown.",
    "Brush top with honey, bake an additional 5-10 minutes for gooey effect.",
    "Serve warm."
